# Week 5 Task 4 — Object Detection on Test Images

## Objective
Using trained YOLO weights to detect bottles on unseen test images.

## Prediction Command

```bash
yolo detect predict model=runs/detect/train/weights/best.pt source=dataset/images/test
```

## Work Completed
- Loaded trained YOLO weights
- Performed object detection on test dataset
- Generated bounding box predictions

## Output
- Predicted images with bounding boxes
- Confidence scores
- Detection results

## Tools Used
- Ultralytics YOLO

## Outcome
Successfully detected bottles in unseen test images using the trained custom model.
